# Lab 1: Basic Small Business Network

## Objective
Build a simple office network and verify communication between devices.

## Devices Used
- 1 Router
- 1 Switch
- 4 PCs
- 1 Server

## IP Scheme
- 192.168.10.0/24

## What I Configured
- Router LAN interface
- IP addresses on all hosts
- Default gateway on all end devices

## Verification
- Successful pings between hosts
- Successful ping to router

## What I Learned
- How end devices use a default gateway
- Basic LAN addressing
- How to test connectivity
